    "@value" : "This class comprise instances of V21 Unvcertainty Grade that could be assigned to a V17 Source."
  } ],
  "http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label" : [ {
    "@language" : "en",
    "@value" : "V21 Uncertainty Grade"
  } ],
  "http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf" : [ {
    "@id" : "http://www.cidoc-crm.org/cidoc-crm/E55_Type"
  } ],
  "http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#notation" : [ {
    "@value" : "V21"
  } ],
  "http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#prefLabel" : [ {
    "@language" : "en",
    "@value" : "Uncertainty Grade"
  } ]
}, {
  "@id" : "https://github.com/elisabettacaterina/CRMvr/V22_Accuracy_Grade",
  "@type" : [ "http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class" ],
  "http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment" : [ {
    "@language" : "en",
    "@value" : "This class comprise instances of V22 Accuracy Grade that could be assigned to a V17 Source."
  } ],
  "http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label" : [ {
    "@language" : "en",
    "@value" : "V22 Accuracy Grade"
  } ],
  "http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf" : [ {
    "@id" : "http://www.cidoc-crm.org/cidoc-crm/E55_Type"
  } ],
  "http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#notation" : [ {
    "@value" : "V22"
  } ],
  "http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#prefLabel" : [ {
    "@language" : "en",
    "@value" : "Accuracy Grade"
  } ]
}, {
  "@id" : "https://github.com/elisabettacaterina/CRMvr/V23_Dimension_Equivalent",
  "@type" : [ "http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class" ],
  "http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment" : [ {
    "@language" : "en",
    "@value" : "This class comprises equivalent value that can be attribute to an E54 Dimension according with the modelling software used. The 3D modelling software usually does not use the same E54 Dimension values and units indicated on a V17 source or E31 Document available."
  } ],
  "http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label" : [ {
    "@language" : "en",
    "@value" : "V23 Dimension Equivalent"
  } ],
  "http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf" : [ {
    "@id" : "http://www.cidoc-crm.org/cidoc-crm/E54_Dimension"
  } ],
  "http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#notation" : [ {
    "@value" : "V23"
  } ],
  "http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#prefLabel" : [ {
    "@language" : "en",
    "@value" : "Dimension Equivalent"
  } ]
}, {
  "@id" : "https://github.com/elisabettacaterina/CRMvr/V24_Type_of_Dimension_Provenance",
  "@type" : [ "http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class" ],
  "http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment" : [ {
    "@language" : "en",
    "@value" : "This class comprises Type of Dimensions in relation withw their reference V17 Sources or E31 Documents. In Virtual Reconstruction Processes are defined ony three enumerated Types of Dimension Provenance: Indicated, Deducted, Interpreted."
  } ],
  "http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label" : [ {
    "@language" : "en",
    "@value" : "V24 Type of Dimension Provenance"
  } ],
  "http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf" : [ {
    "@id" : "http://www.cidoc-crm.org/cidoc-crm/E55_Type"
  } ],
  "http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#notation" : [ {
    "@value" : "V24"
  } ],
  "http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#prefLabel" : [ {
    "@language" : "en",
    "@value" : "Type of Dimension Provenance"
  } ]
}, {
  "@id" : "https://github.com/elisabettacaterina/CRMvr/V25_Evaluation_of_Dimension_Provenance",
  "@type" : [ "http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class" ],
  "http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment" : [ {
    "@language" : "en",
    "@value" : "This class comprises the action of make propositions about Dimension Provenance: connecting the E45 Dimension and its values with a V17 Source or E31 Document used for the Virtual Recontruction."
  } ],
  "http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label" : [ {
